{
  "stem": "753.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What if somebody starts questioning, why aren't you taking this Holy Ghost?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] As I told you, these were days-- the most macabre days for me, loneliness, nothing to do.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The only refuge for me was to go to sleep because these were a few hours that I didn't know anything, that I didn't-- wasn't bored.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was longing for a girlfriend or to see my girlfriends again.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The isolation was tough.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the lack of identity or to do what every teenager does was very, very hard.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But you do what you have to do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You survive.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the name of the game was the survival.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was writing a, a romance.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I still have it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the way it was written, it was in such an Italian that I probably wouldn't understand half of it today.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was the language of the-- scholarly language.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's how I wrote because that's what I read-- those type of books I read.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that gave me a lot of pleasure.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was-- I was-- in that book, in that story, I was describing a boy who lives in a castle-- that was very interesting-- who is blind.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because I felt like this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I felt like I'm blind.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't-- cannot see anything out of this place where I am.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I'm in a-- in a castle.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I'm never out of that castle.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I'm totally isolated.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And this was the story.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I was putting myself into his personality.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Then I was weaving those baskets and trying to sell them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I was helping the farmers when they-- when the time was for the grapes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I don't know how you say it in-- when the grapes were--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
